= SDL_GetRGB =
Use this function to map a pixel value into the RGB components for a given pixel format.
Get RGB values from a pixel in the specified pixel format. 


== Syntax ==
```c++
void SDL_GetRGB(Uint32                 pixel,
                const SDL_PixelFormat* format,
                Uint8*                 r, 
                Uint8*                 g, 
                Uint8*                 b)
```

